                        <p> He Fails Me is the solo music entity of Roger Camero. In 2003, during touring downtime with the band,
                            No Motiv, HFM was created with the sole purpose of Roger writing and recording songs for fun.
                            There was no desire to turn the project from a one man band into a live performance band. During
                            2003-2013, several songs were written and recorded by Roger, only to be shared with a few close
                            friends who were interested in listening. </p>
                    </div>
